    `,
  },
  {
    image: "03/securite-monitoring.png",
    alt: "Monitoring & Security",
    title: "Monitoring <br>& <span>Security</span>",
    description: `
      Our cloud security service in Morocco provides <b>comprehensive protection</b> against internal and external threats, ensures rigorous access management, strengthens governance and data compliance, while <b>guaranteeing rapid recovery</b> in the event of a disaster.
    `,
  },
  {
    image: "03/conformite-anrt.png",
    alt: "Regulatory compliance",
    title: "Regulatory <br><span>compliance</span>",
