    ],
  },
  {
    question: "What's the difference between shared hosting and Cloud VPS?",
    answers: [
      "Our shared cloud hosting solution is based on sharing system resources (CPU, RAM, etc.) between multiple websites hosted on the same server. In contrast, with a Cloud VPS, you benefit from dedicated, guaranteed, and isolated resources. On the shared platform, we manage the entire configuration, including security and the hosting environment.",
      "However, Cloud VPS users are responsible for these technical aspects—unless they choose to delegate them to our experts.",
    ],
  },
  {
    question: "How long does it take to activate my shared hosting plan?",
    answers: [
      "There is no delay in the delivery of your Cloud Morocco hosting package. The activation time mainly depends on the payment method used. For example, credit card payments allow for instant activation of your hosting package.",
