    question: "How long does it take to deliver my Cloud VPS server?",
    answers: [
      "Cloud Morocco VPS servers are custom-configured to meet each client's specific needs.",
      "Delivery time depends on both the payment method used and how quickly you provide the necessary details, which should first be discussed with our sales team.",
    ],
  },
